    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using CDN"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "The simplest way to use Vue is by including it directly via CDN."
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/vue@3\"></script>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using Vite (Recommended)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Vite is the modern and fastest way to create Vue applications."
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "npm create vite@latest my-vue-app\ncd my-vue-app\nnpm install\nnpm run dev"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Using Vue CLI"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Vue CLI is a traditional tool for creating Vue projects with predefined configurations."
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "bash",
      "value": "npm install -g @vue/cli\nvue create my-app\ncd my-app\nnpm run serve"
